ll a `requirements.txt` from the submodule\r\n- [ ] Update the repo to have the plugins repo as a submodule\r\n- [ ] Update the plugin loading script to only load the folder if it is from our repo (maybe)\r\n- [ ] Setup a pipeline to support updating the submodule every release (maybe)\r\n- [ ] Update the documentation to show this in the \r\n    - Install guide\r\n    - plugin guide\r\n    - plugin repo\r\n    - wiki", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Significant-Gravitas/Auto-GPT/issues/3654/reactions", "total_count": 1, "+1": 1, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Significant-Gravitas/Auto-GPT/issues/3654/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}